OL,3,CCharles 'raising a dram' after Trump
OL,4,Cvows to lift Scottish whisky tariffs
OL,6,FThe King will be toasting Donald Trump
OL,7,Fwith a dram after the US president
OL,8,Fannounced he will remove tariffs from
OL,9,FScottish whisky.
OL,11,FMr Trump said it was Charles and
OL,12,FCamilla's intervention that prompted
OL,13,Fthe decision soon after they said
OL,14,Ftheir goodbyes at the end of their
OL,15,Fstate visit to America.
OL,17,FMark Kent, chief executive of the
OL,18,FScottish Distillers Association (SWA),
OL,19,Fsaid "distillers can breathe a little
OL,20,Feasier" following the move.
OL,26,@{D@FOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
