PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777619131
OL,3,CCharles 'raising a dram' after Trump
OL,4,Cvows to lift Scottish whisky tariffs
OL,6,FThe development will vindicate Downing
OL,7,FStreet's decision to send the King on
OL,8,Fa trip, viewed by some as highly
OL,9,Frisky, to repair the UK-US special
OL,10,Frelationship.
OL,12,FMr Trump said that while "people have
OL,13,Fwanted to do this for a long time" the
OL,14,FKing and Queen "got me to do something
OL,15,Fthat nobody else was able to do".
OL,26,@tD@ZOUuD@bO]vD@POUwD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
