OL,3,CCharles 'raising a dram' after Trump
OL,4,Cvows to lift Scottish whisky tariffs
OL,6,FBusiness and Trade Secretary Peter
OL,7,FKyle said: "This is great news for our
OL,8,Fscotch whisky industry, which is worth
OL,9,Falmost #1bn in exports and supports
OL,10,Fthousands of jobs across the UK.
OL,12,F"I have been advocating for lower
OL,13,Ftariffs on key exports like whisky, to
OL,14,Fprotect vital jobs and iconic British
OL,15,Fbrands while strengthening our
OL,16,Frelationship with the US."
OL,26,@oD@LOUtD@AOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
