OL,3,CCharles 'raising a dram' after Trump
OL,4,Cvows to lift Scottish whisky tariffs
OL,6,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper also
OL,7,Fwelcomed the announcement, saying on
OL,8,FX: "We've been working for many months
OL,9,Fto secure this outcome for a key
OL,10,Findustry which supports thousands of
OL,11,Fjobs."
OL,13,FThe White House and Number 10 have
OL,14,Fappeared to be at loggerheads with the
OL,15,Fpresident regularly lambasting the
OL,16,FPrime Minister about his stance over
OL,17,Fthe US-Israeli war against Iran.
OL,26,@pD@DOUsD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
