OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777619131
OL,3,CCharles 'raising a dram' after Trump
OL,4,Cvows to lift Scottish whisky tariffs
OL,6,FBut he has developed a rapport with
OL,7,Fthe King and has heaped praise on
OL,8,F"fantastic" Charles and the UK's
OL,9,Fhistorical ties with the US throughout
OL,10,Fthe trip and at one point was
OL,11,Fphotographed affectionately touching
OL,12,FCharles's knee.
OL,14,FThe monarchy's soft power diplomacy is
OL,15,Fseen as its strongest weapon in
OL,16,Fsupport of the UK's overseas interests
OL,17,Fand it appears Mr Trump has been won
OL,18,Fover.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
