OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777619131
OL,3,CCharles 'raising a dram' after Trump
OL,4,Cvows to lift Scottish whisky tariffs
OL,6,FConfirming the news, Mr Trump posted
OL,7,Fon his Truth Social platform: "In
OL,8,Fhonor of the King and Queen of the
OL,9,FUnited Kingdom, who have just left the
OL,10,FWhite House, soon headed back to their
OL,11,Fwonderful Country, I will be removing
OL,12,Fthe Tariffs and Restrictions on
OL,13,FWhiskey having to do with Scotland's
OL,14,Fability to work with the Commonwealth
OL,15,Fof Kentucky on Whiskey and Bourbon,
OL,16,Ftwo very important Industries within
OL,17,FScotland and Kentucky.
OL,26,@oD@_OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
