PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777619131
OL,3,CCharles 'raising a dram' after Trump
OL,4,Cvows to lift Scottish whisky tariffs
OL,6,F"People have wanted to do this for a
OL,7,Flong time, in that there had been
OL,8,Fgreat Inter-Country Trade, especially
OL,9,Fhaving to do with the Wooden Barrels
OL,10,Fused. The King and Queen got me to do
OL,11,Fsomething that nobody else was able to
OL,12,Fdo, without hardly even asking!
OL,14,F"A wonderful Honor to have them both
OL,15,Fin the U.S.A. President DONALD J.
OL,16,FTRUMP."
OL,18,FMr Trump's previous 25% Scotch tariff
OL,19,Fbetween 2019 and 2021 resulted in the
OL,20,Fsector losing more than #600 million,
OL,21,For #1 million a day, the SWA said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
