FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777619131
OL,3,CCharles 'raising a dram' after Trump
OL,4,Cvows to lift Scottish whisky tariffs
OL,6,FThe SWA has estimated the current 10%
OL,7,Ftariffs are costing whisky firms #3m
OL,8,Fin lost exports each week.
OL,10,FMr Kent said: "This deal is a
OL,11,Fsignificant boost for the Scotch
OL,12,Fwhisky industry in our most valuable
OL,13,Fexport market. Distillers can breathe
OL,14,Fa little easier during a period of
OL,15,Fsignificant pressure on the sector.
OL,17,F"We are hugely grateful for the
OL,18,Fsustained efforts on both sides of the
OL,19,FAtlantic. For months, many have worked
OL,20,Ftirelessly to return zero-for-zero
OL,21,Ftariff trade for whisky and bourbon.
OL,26,@rD@OOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
