OL,3,CCharles 'raising a dram' after Trump
OL,4,Cvows to lift Scottish whisky tariffs
OL,6,F"The special relationship that the
OL,7,FScotch Whisky and American Whiskey
OL,8,Findustries share will be reinvigorated
OL,9,Fby this announcement."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@VO]
